rows.label: qst400201_msg0002
rows.name:
But Gabugabu is an informant by
trade, mo. I can't just provide
information for free, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0004
rows.name:
A Gulan girl is being held
prisoner on the Divine
Beast battleship, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0005
rows.name:
Unfortunately, Gabugabu doesn't
have a name yet, mo...

rows.label: qst400201_msg0006
rows.name:
But there's a rumor that the
big ship came here just to
imprison that one girl, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0007
rows.name:
The people of Torigo are getting
along fine with the Empire, so
we don't want any trouble...

rows.label: qst400201_msg0008
rows.name:
That seems to be what most
residents of Torigo think, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0009
rows.name:
...That's all the information
Gabugabu has, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0010
rows.name: Was that enough to satisfy you, mo?

rows.label: qst400201_msg0011
rows.name:
I'm offering a massive discount,
and you still won't buy, mo?

rows.label: qst400201_msg0012
rows.name:
If you're short on cash, you
should go outside town and
defeat some monsters, mo.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0013
rows.name:
I'd normally charge for that
info, too, but I'll let you
have it for free this time, mo.
